# Sporting Health Club - Django demo

This is a minimal Django project with an `accounts` app that provides:

- Login page
- Logout page
- Dashboard (placeholder)
- A management command to create role groups: Receptionist, Manager, Owner, Admin

Quick start (Windows PowerShell):

1. Create a virtualenv and activate it

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

2. Run migrations and create a superuser

```powershell
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser
```

3. Create role groups

```powershell
python manage.py create_roles
```

4. Run the dev server

```powershell
python manage.py runserver
```

Visit http://127.0.0.1:8000/ to go to the dashboard (will redirect to login if not authenticated).
